text: Warwick is an unincorporated community in Klickitat County, in the U.S. state of Washington. ==History== A post office called Warwick was established in 1904, and remained in operation until 1906. The community has the name of W. S. Warwick, a local cattleman. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Klickitat County, Washington Category:Unincorporated communities in Washington (state)
title: Warwick, Washington
